conversion_rate.query: leads = load "${App.Datasets.lead_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; converted = filter leads by 'IsConverted' == "True"; converted = group converted by all; converted = foreach converted generate count() as 'count_converted'; leads = group leads by all; leads = foreach leads generate count() as 'count_all'; q = group leads by all full, converted by all; q = foreach q generate sum(leads['count_all']) as 'count_all', sum(converted['count_converted']) as 'count_converted'; q = foreach q generate coalesce('count_converted' / 'count_all', 0) as 'sum_percent';

content.displayTemplate: Drill down into key factors contributing to higher lead conversion rates.
